        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         The change to Innate Regen happened a while back. It only affected Iksars and Trolls. Originally, these races got regen at 2hp per tick for each point, instead of the 1hp/tick that all other races got. This was changed to be the same as everyone elses later on.</P><P>Seems they did actually listen to Xzzy's complaints even back then.</P><P>Tenaiya Soulscorcher<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
